name: Part Reflecting Whole, 2021
description: On April 29th, 2021, the Compusophy Discord server and Twitter account were taken offline by the artist of mention. In Compusophy's absence, a collective of patrons remain hopeful for their return. Nine hundred and thirty metaglass cubes are placed by hand to form an incomplete structure. On its face, "part reflecting whole" is expressed with a cipher designed for metasculpture.
